%section#hero
  / Flex Container
  .container.flex.flex-col-reverse.items-center.px-6.mx-auto.mt-10.space-y-0.md:space-y-0.md:flex-row
    / Left Item
    .flex.flex-col.mb-32.space-y-12{:class => "md:w-1/2"}
      %h1.max-w-md.text-4xl.font-bold.text-center.md:text-5xl.md:text-left
        A better way to take surveys
      %p.max-w-sm.text-center.text-darkGrayishBlue.md:text-left
        CloutCloud is the "anti-panel" that compensates micro-influencers for both their opinions and influence.
      .flex.justify-center.md:justify-start
        %button.p-3.px-6.pt-2.text-white.bg-brightRed.rounded-full.baseline.hover.bg-brightRedLight= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_path
    / Image
    %div{:class => "bg-[url('stacked-waves.svg')]"}
/ Features Section
%section#feature
  / Flex container
  .container.flex.flex-col.px-4.mx-auto.mt-10.space-y-12.med:space-y-0.md:flex-row
    .flex.flex-col.space-y-12{:class => "md:w-1/2"}
      / What's Different
      %h2.max-w-md.text-4xl.font-bold.text-center.md:text-left
        What's different about CloutCloud?
      %p.max-w-sm.text-center.text-darkGrayishBlue.md:text-left
        CloutCloud flips the model of traditional consumer panels by giving the lion's share of compensation to survey participants and rewards them even when they don't qualify for surveys.
    %div
      / Numbered List
      .flex.flex-col.space-y-8{:class => "md:w-1/2"}
        / List item 1
        .flex.flex-col.space-y-3.md:space-y-0.md:space-x-6.md:flex-row
          .rounded-l-full.bg-brightRedSupLight.md:bg-transparent
            .flex.items-center.space-x-2
              .px-4.py-2.text-white.rounded-full.md:py-1.bg-brightRed
                01
              %h3.text-base.font-bold.md:mb-4.md:hidden
                Earn More for Your Opinion
          %div
            %h3.hidden.mb-4.text-lg.font-bold.md:block
              Earn More for Your Opinion
            %p.text-darkGrayishBlue
              Unlike typical consumer research panels, that reap 80-90% of panelist fees, CloutCloud flips the model and pays the bulk to participants.
        .flex.flex-col.space-y-3.md:space-y-0.md:space-x-6.md:flex-row
          .rounded-l-full.bg-brightRedSupLight.md:bg-transparent
            .flex.items-center.space-x-2
              .px-4.py-2.text-white.rounded-full.md:py-1.bg-brightRed
                02
              %h3.text-base.font-bold.md:mb-4.md:hidden
                Share to Earn As Well
          %div
            %h3.hidden.mb-4.text-lg.font-bold.md:block
              Share to Earn As Well
            %p.text-darkGrayishBlue
              Leverage your influence by referring others to take surveys. It's win-win as they get paid to complete the survey and you get paid for referring them.
        .flex.flex-col.space-y-3.md:space-y-0.md:space-x-6.md:flex-row
          .rounded-l-full.bg-brightRedSupLight.md:bg-transparent
            .flex.items-center.space-x-2
              .px-4.py-2.text-white.rounded-full.md:py-1.bg-brightRed
                03
              %h3.text-base.font-bold.md:mb-4.md:hidden
                Make the Most of Your Time
          %div
            %h3.hidden.mb-4.text-lg.font-bold.md:block
              Make the Most of Your Time
            %p.text-darkGrayishBlue
              Panels can be frustrating especially when you attempt to take a survey, don't qualify and don't get paid. CloutCloud ensures you earn, whether you qualify or not. 
